  "code": "stateDiagram\n  [*]-->Creating\n  Creating-->Writer\n  Creating-->Reader\n  Creating-->[*]\n  state Writer {\n    [*]-->Writing\n    Writing-->Disconnecting\n    Disconnecting-->ClosingReader\n    ClosingReader-->Creating\n  }\n  state Reader {\n    [*]-->Reading\n    Reading-->Error\n    Error-->ClosingWriter\n    ClosingWriter-->Creating  \n  }",
