  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个连接管理的状态图。系统启动后先进入Creating状态，然后可能分叉成Writer或Reader两条线，也可能直接结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Creating是入口后的第一个状态。那Writer和Reader是并行关系还是分支？另外您说的\"直接结束\"是指Creating可以直接回到终止状态吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Creating可以分支到Writer或Reader，也可以直接结束。Writer和Reader是两个独立的子状态机，各自内部有详细流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：起始点到Creating，Creating分出三条线——到Writer、到Reader、以及回到终止。现在展开Writer内部，您说怎么设计？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Writer内部从初始状态进入Writing，然后到Disconnecting，再到ClosingReader，最后回到Creating。注意是ClosingReader不是ClosingWriter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Writer",
        "Writing",
        "Disconnecting",
        "ClosingReader",
        "Creating"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "ClosingReader？这个命名有点反直觉，Writer内部关闭Reader？不过按您的要求画。那Reader内部呢，也是类似结构吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ClosingReader",
        "Writer",
        "Reader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Reader内部是Reading，然后可能进入Error状态，再到ClosingWriter，最后也回到Creating。这里是对称的——Writer里关Reader，Reader里关Writer。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reader",
        "Reading",
        "Error",
        "ClosingWriter",
        "Creating"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，交叉关闭的设计。我画一下：Reader内部从初始到Reading，异常时到Error，然后ClosingWriter，最终回到Creating。这样两边都闭环回到Creating，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Reader",
        "Reading",
        "Error",
        "ClosingWriter",
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "ClosingReader"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个结构。Creating作为中心枢纽，Writer和Reader两个子状态机处理完各自流程后都回到这里，可以重新创建新的连接。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Creating",
        "Writer",
        "Reader",
        "ClosingReader",
        "ClosingWriter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
